properties.Name: CreditStatusType
properties.Description:
A credit status that may be applied for a period to reflect credit-worthiness.

Ex:
- Excellent
- Above Average
- Average
- Below Average
- Poor
- Unrated 
- Credit available for purchases
- Credit purchases require management approval
- Credit denied to future purchases
- Requires management approval
